      <section name='catch'>

         <para number='1' comment='Catch zombie - have chatted'>
         What good would it do you to take Cedric captive now? And what has he done to deserve such treatment?
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Have tried before'>
         Trying to take the zombie prisoner didn't work when you tried it before; what makes you think you will succeed a second time?
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Try to catch with lasso'>
         You twirl the lasso around a few times and then hurl it at the zombie. It looks like a good throw, but the zombie, despite its clumsy demeanor, manages to avoid it. It glares at you, and says, "Hey, cut that out, willya?"
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Try to catch with bandages'>
         You try to fling a length of bandages around the zombie in order to catch it, but it just doesn't work. Maybe you need to knot them so they form some kind of lasso.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Try to catch bare-handed'>
