         It's a big old-fashioned-looking computer, made out of a dull grey plastic, with lots of flashing LEDs on the front which presumably indicate something important to those that need to know. There's a screen in the middle, and a keyboard sitting on a small shelf. A post-it note has been stuck to the edge of the screen.
