      <section name='keyboard'>

         <para number='1' comment='Get keyboard'>
         You pick up the keyboard but you can't take it away because it's attached to the shelf by a short curly wire. However, you notice that there is a sticker on the bottom that says: Frankenstein.
         </para>

      </section>

      <section name='misc'>

