      <section name='death'>

         <para number='1' comment='Player falls into open grave'>
         Suddenly you tumble into an open grave, landing badly and bashing your head on a partially-buried rock. The fatal wound makes the earth walls of the grave seem to close in around you...
         </para>

      </section>

