         <para number='1' comment='Spooky sound 1'>
         Lightning forks across the sky above you, accompanied by a cacophonous clap of thunder which echoes back and forth before dying away.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Spooky sound 2'>
         Thunder rumbles in the distance, rolling around the landscape, seeming to circle your position until it gets back to its point of origin and stops.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Spooky sound 3'>
         The misty air is riven with a piercingly high howl, that of some demented creature or dangerous animal.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Spooky sound 4'>
         You hear a strange creaking noise, but you can't tell where it is coming from. It continues for a few moments and then stops just as suddenly.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Spooky sound 5'>
         A low moaning sound echoes around, the sound of some poor creature in terrible despair.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Spooky sound 6'>
         A high-pitched scream, that of somebody suffering the most terrible torment, hangs in the air for a moment before dying away.
         </para>

      </section>

