      <section name='board'>

         <para number='1' comment='Control 1814 - get noticeboard'>
         The noticeboard has been firmly fixed to the wall, so you can't pick it up. If you want to see what is on the board, read it.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Read noticeboard - option 1'>
         A scrap of paper contains the one word: Eureka!
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Option 2'>
         On one of the pieces of paper, someone has used a thick black magic marker to draw a spiral.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Option 3'>
         A piece of paper torn out of a magazine or newspaper has a picture of the Galactic Trading Guild headquarters building on Earth. Somebody has scribbled all over it in red pen.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Option 4'>
         The words 'klaatu barada nikto' have been jotted onto what looks like a paper napkin.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Option 5'>
         The take-away menu from the Sizzling Wok on Mercury has been pinned to the board.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Option 6'>
         A page has been torn out of a scholarly book of some kind. The only words on it you can understand are 'The' and 'A' - the rest might as well be written in Martian!
